Data

First, load packages and read in the data from the FIXME data processing.

library(tidyverse)
library(gm)
library(music)
load("../data/monthly_weather")
source("../code/data_to_soniof_all.R")

Code

## create smaller subset of 5 years for testing
test_data <- monthly_weather %>% filter(between(year, 1910, 1915))

Monthly Data

12/8
durations = rep("eighth", times = nrow(test_data))
pitches = data_to_sonif_all(test_data$mean, low = 3, high = 4)

line_avg <- Line(pitches = pitches, durations = durations, 
                 name = "Monthly Average")

music_12_8 <- Music() + Meter(12, 8) + 
     line_avg + 
     Instrument(42, 1) +  
  Tempo(120) 

gm::show(music_12_8, to = c("score", "audio"))

gm::export(music_12_8, "12_8.mscz")
8/8
durations = pattern = rep(c(rep(rep("quarter/3", times = 3), times = 4)), 
              times = nrow(test_data)/12)
pitches = data_to_sonif_all(test_data$mean, low = 3, high = 4)

line_avg <- Line(pitches = pitches, durations = durations, 
                 name = "Monthly Average")

music_8_8 <- Music() + Meter(8, 8) + 
     line_avg + 
     Instrument(42, 1) +  
  Tempo(120) 

gm::show(music_8_8, to = c("score", "audio"))

#gm::export(music_8_8, "8_8.mscz")
